name: Discord.js + Noblox.js Example Bot
description: (Made by MrCoolGuy2008WoW on roblox and OkBoomer#3424 on discord) Example for a discord/roblox rank bot.

TOKEN.description: A Secret Bot Token, Used To Login The BOT. Get The Token In Your App Settings.

PREFIX.description: A Prefix To Run Your Bot Commands.

MINRANK.description: The minimum someone can be ranked

MAXRANK.description: The maximum someone can be ranked

GROUPID.description: The Id of the group you want your rank bot want to rank.
